   "serial no":1302

Option:
"level":1 => access defined area
"level":2 => leave defined area
"level":3 => stay defined area over time

{
   "content":"tag led config",
   "gateway id":137205,
   "id":23349,
   "on time(1ms)":20,
   "off time(1ms)":10000,
   "serial no":1302
}
on time = 0 ~ 65535; 0 = LED off, no flashing
off time = 0 ~ 65535; 0 = LED on, no flashing
"total" item is the total number of JSON messages needed to send for the image. Max. = 45.
"current" is order number of this JSON message
"data" item is base 64 encoded image data
